column5: 1.我會認真聆聽上課所說的一切(I listen carefully to everything that is said in class)
column6: 2.對於不會的問題我會向老師提問(I ask questions about what I do not know.)
column7: 3.我會在上課期間與同學互動(I interact with my peers during class.)
column8: 4.我會盡可能地在上課期間就學會課程內容(I strive to understand lessons during class.)
column9: 5.我很專心上課(I am alert during class.)
column10: 6.我總是和老師一起討論(I always participate in discussions with my teacher.)
column11: 7.我總是很想去上課(I am always eager to attend class.)
column12: 8.我總是能完成我的作業(I always complete my assignments.)
column13: 9.我更喜歡在上課時與老師還有同伴一起完成活動和作業(I prefer to complete activities and assignments during class with my instructor and peers.)
column14: 10.課堂上有足夠的時間進行練習和討論(Enough time is provided during class for practice activities and discussions.)
column15: 11.我總是詢問老師困難的課程內容(I always ask the instructor about difficult content.)
column16: 12.我會嘗試運用課程上所學到的東西 (I attempt to apply things that I learned during class.)
column17: 13.我會與同學討論我在家裡學到的東西(I relate to my peers and discuss with them what I learned at home.)
column18: 14.我努力在在這門課上獲得新知識(I strive to acquire new knowledge about the course.)
column19: 15.在上課前先了解課程內容會激勵我並增加我的參與度(Being familiar with the content prior to attending class motivates me and increases my engagement.)
column20: 16.事先準備課程可以讓我更好的與老師和同學溝通(Preparing for lessons enables me to communicate better with my peers and the instructor.)
column21: 17.在上課前先了解課程內容會有助於我在課堂上與同學分享我所學到的(Familiarizing myself with content prior to attending a lecture enables me to share what I learned with others during class.)
column22: 18.我喜歡這門課(I enjoy the class.)
column23: 19.老師使用的教學方法是有樂趣的(The teaching method practiced by the instructor is enjoyable.)
column24: 20.我喜歡課堂上進行的學習活動(I enjoy the practice activities conducted during class.)
column25: 21.我喜歡在家學習(I enjoy studying content at home.)
column26: 22.我喜歡老師問我問題(I like it when the instructor asks me questions.)
column27: 23.我喜歡在上課前先對課程內容有所了解(I am optimistic when I go to class with an understanding of the content.)
column28: 24.參加課堂討論會增加我的信心(Participating in class discussions boosts my confidence.)
column29: 25.在課堂上解決以及分享問題是很愉快的(Solving and sharing problems during class is enjoyable.)
column30: 在上這門課之前，您是否學習過任何程式語言? 沒有請答無，有的話請填寫您學過哪些程式語言。
column31: 1. 在課前都會概覽(Survey)課程內容。
column32: 2. 我在課前都會針對課程內容進行自我提問(Question)。
column33: 3. 我在課前都有透過詳讀(Read)來預習課程內容。
column34: 4. 我在課堂的總結(Summary)活動，或是課後都會透過回想(Recall)來複習課程內容。
column35: 5. 我在課後，都會針對課程內容進行複習(Review)。
column36: 6. 我覺得SQ3R閱讀策略對我的學習是有幫助的。
